{
  "id": "RAW_6b92868a",
  "title": "何止是“看图写代码”，Kimi K2.5 甚至可以“看视频写代码”！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247500957&idx=1&sn=c6a34ee38894f94fa448bd97d4834fcd",
  "date": "2026-01-27 11:04:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=037d3d81&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlFxqHib6eHkf0d3wKmtmKDggKMODbP6ZTXUoUogeTt1Nia67fOug6CMiavyXibTRpKyefzSkknQk7ibunA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #faf9f7 !important;padding: 20px 24px 40px 24px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前的国产模型似乎都是海外顶级模型的跟随者，这次Kimi K2.5有些不同，它不仅有多模态能力，还做出来了一些Codex 和Claude Code暂时都还做不到的事情——“</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">看视频写代码</span><span leaf=\"\">”。</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 26px;font-weight: 600;margin: 32px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(157, 200, 141) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">省流版</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">亮点</span></strong></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 20px 0;padding-left: 28px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">有多模态能力了。不止“看图写代码”，Kimi K2.5 甚至支持“看视频写代码”</span><span leaf=\"\">！ 其中，‘看视频’目前Codex、Claude Code都无法做到的，支持100M以内的视频文件。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi Agent可以在云端打开一台电脑，完成复杂任务。对于程序员来说，我们可以“根据一条URL，复刻写出代码”，连页面里需要的图片都可以自动生成。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi Code是开源的，方便程序员魔改。看了下代码，是<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">基于Python从零构建</span>的，不是跟风或者抄袭其他Code。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"max-width: 700px;box-sizing: border-box;overflow-wrap: break-word;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\">Kimi 2.5模型本身，也是开源的</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">一些遗憾</span></strong></p>\n   <ol style=\"margin: 20px 0;padding-left: 28px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型本身的编程智能水平和海外顶级模型，在复杂项目当中，仍然有些差距。（如果是小型简单项目，差距倒是不明显。）希望下一代K3中可以解决。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin: 10px 0;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;\">\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi Code的交互设计有个新功能，本意是让用户按Ctrl+X切换bash和agent，但是和用户现有使用Claude Code的习惯不太符合，我用着不是很顺手。你可以试试看，想必如果能够适应新习惯，是很方便的。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面我们开始测试！</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 26px;font-weight: 600;margin: 32px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(157, 200, 141) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装Kimi Code</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">本次测试以Kimi Code为主，后面也使用网页版的功能。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装Kimi Code</span></p>\n   <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Linux / macOS</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">curl -LsSf <a href=\"https://cdn.kimi.com/binaries/kimi-cli/install.sh\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.kimi.com/binaries/kimi-cli/install.sh</a> | bash</span></code><br></pre></code><br></pre>\n   <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);margin:24px 0;overflow:hidden;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-moz-osx-font-smoothing:grayscale;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Windows (PowerShell)</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">Invoke-RestMethod <a href=\"https://cdn.kimi.com/binaries/kimi-cli/install.ps1\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.kimi.com/binaries/kimi-cli/install.ps1</a> | Invoke-Expression</span></code><br></pre></code><br></pre>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们先到 <a href=\"https://www.kimi.com/code\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kimi.com/code</a> 购买套餐。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果是想初步体验，可以先买最便宜的套餐，只需要&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight: 600;color: #C15F3C !important;background-color: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.08) !important;padding: 2px 6px;border-radius: 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.99元</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/ 7天，约等于免费。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果日常每天使用，我推荐购买99元/月的套餐，价格公道，Token量比较够用。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">安装完成后，在命令行输入&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">kimi</span>&nbsp;启动</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\">输入&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\">/login</span>&nbsp;登录即可使用</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 20px 0 !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: #2b2b2b !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15855572998430142\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1274\" style=\"max-height:500px !important;display:block;margin:24px auto;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1);width:100%;\" data-backw=\"482\" data-backh=\"76\" data-imgfileid=\"100017308\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5abb4cc2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFxqHib6eHkf0d3wKmtmKDggnGoXquIGyCDWQT1whsrjbH0NdVFFsoiaOviaIqhKmI6nK6bYXhoT8ymg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"background-color: #faf9f7 !important;padding: 20px 24px 40px 24px;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto;box-sizing: border-box;word-wrap: break-word;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 26px;font-weight: 600;margin: 32px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(157, 200, 141) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">基础模态能力：看图写代码</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">用最简单的Prompt试试：我复制了Toolify首页截图，用Kimi Code输入</span></p>\n   <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 2px 8px;margin:24px 0px;overflow:hidden;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\">复刻这个图片，用html</span></code><br></pre></code><br></pre>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5185185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto;display: block;margin: 24px auto;border-radius: 10px;box-shadow: rgba(193, 95, 60, 0.1) 0px 6px 24px;max-height: 500px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017273\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1cf46e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFxqHib6eHkf0d3wKmtmKDggM34srMSNVBh5JeoRkJiaP2yBYcqusibAWzoYNX5ib5YhnibBP0snlwkMVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">贴图的过程很方便，无论是直接Cmd+V粘贴、文件路径、拖入，都可以。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi Code (with Kimi K2.5)的工作流程很顺利。从输出的思考过程可以看出，它还挺耐心的先拆解了截图的布局，然后再依次拆分控件来写。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.40925925925925927\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017254\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43b76f01&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFxqHib6eHkf0d3wKmtmKDggn6ec5HhAw4ckDvOXZ09ScUcibYXcdFPX07ibicLZtDOP4MYpYWLPrYM8A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3861111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017253\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=92e34db8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFxqHib6eHkf0d3wKmtmKDggicUX0reYXu47M8g3QYibXds8evxsncDovlnfj3RrAv2obspzk5ocPBvw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果如下。 下图：左边是原版截图，右边是Kimi Code复刻的</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">还不错吧？还原度怎么说也在90%以上了。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5185185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017272\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c1cf46e2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFxqHib6eHkf0d3wKmtmKDggM34srMSNVBh5JeoRkJiaP2yBYcqusibAWzoYNX5ib5YhnibBP0snlwkMVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5675925925925925\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-height: 340px !important;width: auto !important;height: auto !important;display: inline-block !important;border-radius: 4px !important;object-fit: contain !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100017256\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9df94b7a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFxqHib6eHkf0d3wKmtmKDggT7qocD5wicdYVGtgXIx5Un2gerypxWibKBscD738icmzVdCm1zRgyeY7Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      </td>\n     </tr>\n    </tbody>\n   </table>\n   <h2 style=\"font-size: 26px;font-weight: 600;margin: 32px 0px 16px;letter-spacing: -0.015em;background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgb(193, 95, 60) 0%, rgb(157, 200, 141) 100%) text;color: rgb(193, 95, 60) !important;line-height: 1.25 !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">亮点：看视频写代码！</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2有‘看视频写代码’这个能力我还挺意外的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">我先录了自己的Twitter的视频，也是同时打开Codex、Claude Code、Kimi Code(with K2.5)进行测试。</span></p>\n   <pre><code><pre style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:0px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15) 0px 2px 8px;margin:24px 0px;overflow:hidden;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"padding:16px 20px;white-space:pre-wrap;display:block;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;SF Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, &quot;Courier New&quot;, monospace;line-height:1.7;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\"><span leaf=\"\">接下来，看这个视频，复刻出来所有主要页面 /Users/liuxiaopai/Downloads/录屏-Twitter主要页面.mp4</span></code><br></pre></code><br></pre>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">显然，Claude Code和Codex是无法完成这个任务的，下图1是Claude Code、图2是Codex。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: -0.005em;margin: 20px 0px !important;line-height: 1.8 !important;color: rgb(43, 43, 43) !important;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这两位海外留学生，都打算采用‘把视频按照每秒1次的频率进行截图，再复刻截图’，进行曲线救国。这不算真正的理解视频。</span></p>\n   <table style=\"width: 100% !important;border-collapse: collapse !important;margin: 20px auto !important;table-layout: fixed !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n    <tbody>\n     <tr>\n      <td style=\"padding: 4px !important;vertical-align: top !important;border: none !important;background: transparent !important;\">\n       <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6759259259259259\" data-